### Test 1: Create a Valid Job Application (New Company & Tags)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyName": "Netflix",
  "title": "Backend Engineer",
  "work_type": "hybrid",
  "status_id": 2,
  "location": "Tel Aviv",
  "tags": ["Node.js", "Express", "REST API"],
  "notes": "Applied through a friend reference"
}

